commit message:
Mapdust Bugs can now be Added (only other)
Cleaned up the code (Changed Bug values are now stored seperately)
New Comments are now shown in the Bug Editor
Save Icon in Bug Editor now only Visible if the Bug contains changes
Bugs will now only be added if an Option was activated in the Menu
Changed Openstreetmap Notes Bug Icons to their Originals
Now only valid States show up in the State Selector
The Edit Icon is now only shown if the Bug is actually Editable
Added Function to load all Comments in Mapdust Bugs

Opening a Bug with Extra Download Data now shows a Progress Dialog to
inform the users
Improvements to Retrieving the Extra Data on Bugs
Set Debug mode to false for Release
